{
  "stem": "14091.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when spring came, and for the third time my brothers came to visit me, I begged them that I would like to come with them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Also, in the same vicinity where the partisans were, lots of Jewish families, survivors, organized.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they lived there in bunkers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They dug from the ground, and it was bunkers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the food they would get that the Jewish boys, the partisans, would go in the night and steal and bring for them, and this how they survived.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I heard about it, and I knew already from my brothers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I started begging them that please, they should take me out of there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Tzila ?] heard that I am going to leave, she decided that she will also leave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she was a grown person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was-- I was too young, and she was an adult.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So when she decided that she will go to the partisans, Piotr arranged for her to get a gun, and he followed her.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was in love with her, and he followed her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He left the family and he arranged for himself and for her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they left, and they went to the partisans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My brother Zalman came, took me, brought me to a group of Jewish family, and parked me there for a time being, until he will arrange for me to get some kind of gun or anything that I could be taking to the-- to the partisans, to-- with him.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It-- we stayed-- I stayed with this family for several months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the Germans decided that they have enough of the partisans, and they couldn't take it because they were fighting very fiercely.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were burning the bridges, and they were burning everything they saw.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
